,"uid":113545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"想開但唔係無啦啦<br />\n幾年前有次搭鐵，有個大隻佬特登亞開兩隻手行入車廂，撞到我同其他人<br />\n成程車亞開對手唔知做乜勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢同一站落車<br />\n一落又特登貼埋嚟用手爭撞我<br />\n我唔忿氣又用手爭撞返佢<br />\n點知佢急步走避開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇住佢好快咁走咗去都冇計，唔追<br />\n不過轉個彎就見到佢喺前面十幾米遠<br />\n同個鬼佬準備開拖<br />\n鬼佬擺晒拳架(似西拳)，有啲緊張咁但唔卸個大隻佬<br />\n大隻佬只敢睥咗幾下就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定個傻仔周圍撞人撞著個堅抽鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0059ba0b8c10b55e85966b4aebe4c4dec2276a7a","tid":2249421,"uid":369713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a6dd06fac5d04333eb271b0889bc95ab672f9b0","tid":2249421,"uid":76603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"我成日都好想一腳踢落啲講支那話既小蝗蟲度<br />\nTell me I&rsquo;m not alone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"Same"},{"pid":"ccce09dfdf5286cd9e6114e7a54a266c1b6ad629","tid":2249421,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a6dd06fac5d04333eb271b0889bc95ab672f9b0","tid":2249421,"uid":76603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"我成日都好想一腳踢落啲講支那話既小蝗蟲度<br />\nTell me I&rsquo;m not alone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n扮睇唔到<br />\n兜腳筆起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa4feef09b59a5f50375f68d7e9d75cfc30425e","tid":2249421,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"你地當下去緊返工係會燥D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撞到果刻將你地內心壓抑既燥底激發左出黎，就大家互相向對方發泄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人之常情黎"},{"pid":"a969a6dfe7ef633b79551e40f3b9bc6f2c028707","tid":2249421,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3